{"tid":581299,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廣深高鐵大停駛】乘客困車廂6粒鐘 激動圍乘務員大喊 ：要落車","createTime":"2018-03-05T08:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T10:35:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad7333f586ff9a6a370bb8725ada9a21210034c","tid":581299,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180305/large/1520233671_d9d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180305%2Flarge%2F1520233671_d9d2.jpg&h=16ce6597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深圳高鐵發生嚴重延誤，無數乘客滯留車站，在途中的列車亦大受影響。網民「Randy_沈」在網上貼文，指自己被困列車內6小時。<br />\n<br />\n「Randy_沈」下午1時許在微博上發帖：「從早晨7:05到中午1:00，延誤近6個小時，還要等多久還未知，很多乘客一直餓著肚子，乘客情緒慢慢變得非常激動，向列車工作人員提出下車」<br />\n<br />\n在其貼文上的影片所見，見一班乘客圍着乘務員，不斷投訴，要求職員回覆一個確切到站時間，不能讓乘客無了期等候。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180305/57906952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57906952&d=ZEo7vQ9fCHK54tDwjZR3fZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=68242a97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57906952&h=3ecd491d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180305/57906952</a>"},{"pid":"268f0ea6ca299ba2e186b4f424dbbe81bc7fe09b","tid":581299,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:35:08.000Z","msg":"高鐵又贏"}]}